.TH "component_bind_all" 9 "component_bind_all" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
component_bind_all \- bind all components of an aggregate driver
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" component_bind_all
.BI "(struct device *master_dev "  ","
.BI "void *data "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "master_dev" 12
device with the aggregate driver
.IP "data" 12
opaque pointer, passed to all components
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Binds all components of the aggregate \fIdev\fP by passing \fIdata\fP to their
\fIcomponent_ops.bind\fP functions. Should be called from
\fIcomponent_master_ops.bind\fP.
